Todo for next release:
======================

Milestone 0.1:
--------------
* Working code (released)


Bugfix release 0.1.1:
---------------------
* Don't recommend LANG=C since it will break unicode output
* add support to specify "[User ID not found]"-String
    * German: [User-ID nicht gefunden]
    * may change, so leave it as parameter!
    * without <-u> either use english or try to detect language

Bugfix release 0.1.2:
---------------------
* Date paramter now takes ISO8601.
* Fixed issue with date rounding when running with sigs/keys from the current date.
* Fixed code related to all-keys parameter. This breaks previous default behavior.

Milestone 0.2:
--------------
* more sophisticated checking of input
    => break if --no-with-colons detected
    => break earlier, if wrong input is detected (especially for --date).
* Strike through keys not created yet

Milestone 0.3:
--------------
